{"lang":"zh","stage":2,"title":"still short + simple (up to 5 words)","sentences":[{"t":"你应该吃点东西。","en":"You should eat.","r":"Nǐ yīnggāi chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_4b7e63f99e2b.mp3"},{"t":"我现在就走。","en":"I'm leaving now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài jiù zǒu.","a":"n_5e9adac62e06.mp3"},{"t":"我做运动。","en":"I do sports.","r":"Wǒ zuò yùndòng.","a":"n_7cc8e4a895a7.mp3"},{"t":"你做运动吗？","en":"Do you play sports?","r":"Nǐ zuò yùndòng ma?","a":"n_79ff8dda6840.mp3"},{"t":"很高兴认识你。","en":"Pleased to meet you.","r":"Hěn gāoxìng rènshi nǐ.","a":"n_1f7295fdc12b.mp3"},{"t":"你们准备好了吗？","en":"Are you guys ready?","r":"Nǐmen zhǔnbèi hǎo le ma?","a":"n_cc2c31ce3707.mp3"},{"t":"你跟我一起来吗？","en":"Are you coming with me?","r":"Nǐ gēn wǒ yìqǐ lái ma?","a":"n_95cc3409c542.mp3"},{"t":"我渴了。","en":"I'm thirsty.","r":"Wǒ kě le.","a":"n_86ebcd7fce64.mp3"},{"t":"你在说什么？","en":"What are you saying?","r":"Nǐ zài shuō shénme?","a":"n_b57570565208.mp3"},{"t":"她可以。","en":"She can.","r":"Tā kěyǐ.","a":"n_5adff4aea5bd.mp3"},{"t":"我可以进来吗？","en":"Can I come in?","r":"Wǒ kěyǐ jìnlái ma?","a":"n_307f95634078.mp3"},{"t":"你看到了吗？","en":"Did you see it?","r":"Nǐ kàndào le ma?","a":"n_7df960e18f51.mp3"},{"t":"我穿衣服。","en":"I get dressed.","r":"Wǒ chuān yīfu.","a":"n_0fb9d500dc12.mp3"},{"t":"你有咖啡吗？","en":"Do you have coffee?","r":"Nǐ yǒu kāfēi ma?","a":"n_3cd5b4569171.mp3"},{"t":"我们住在一起。","en":"We live together.","r":"Wǒmen zhù zài yìqǐ.","a":"n_46fcc4b13447.mp3"},{"t":"你住在哪儿？","en":"Where do you live?","r":"Nǐ zhù zài nǎr?","a":"n_a1c7856e74a9.mp3"},{"t":"你住得远吗？","en":"Do you live far away?","r":"Nǐ zhù de yuǎn ma?","a":"n_b9edfd678095.mp3"},{"t":"我们累了。","en":"We're tired.","r":"Wǒmen lèi le.","a":"n_fd5212474a05.mp3"},{"t":"出太阳了。","en":"It's sunny.","r":"Chū tàiyáng le.","a":"n_b8dc436cb297.mp3"},{"t":"我很快回来。","en":"I'll be back soon.","r":"Wǒ hěn kuài huílái.","a":"n_e97e59676d27.mp3"},{"t":"你能帮我吗？","en":"Can you help me?","r":"Nǐ néng bāng wǒ ma?","a":"n_d71696f1b1cd.mp3"},{"t":"我得走了。","en":"I must go.","r":"Wǒ děi zǒu le.","a":"n_e8843c4636ee.mp3"},{"t":"我可以试试。","en":"I can try.","r":"Wǒ kěyǐ shìshi.","a":"n_8dd37c873cec.mp3"},{"t":"过来。","en":"Come here.","r":"Guòlái.","a":"n_b9720a9ceab5.mp3"},{"t":"我现在到了。","en":"I'm here now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài dào le.","a":"n_abf4920d89b0.mp3"},{"t":"怎么了？","en":"What happened?","r":"Zěnme le?","a":"n_ec54a51dc20b.mp3"},{"t":"你看得到我吗？","en":"Can you see me?","r":"Nǐ kàn de dào wǒ ma?","a":"n_24bb7ef4df5f.mp3"},{"t":"你在找什么？","en":"What are you looking for?","r":"Nǐ zài zhǎo shénme?","a":"n_23218b49b001.mp3"},{"t":"我发烧了。","en":"I have a fever.","r":"Wǒ fāshāo le.","a":"n_c8cadb0fa18c.mp3"},{"t":"我咳嗽。","en":"I have a cough.","r":"Wǒ késòu.","a":"n_5995f86db41c.mp3"},{"t":"我是墨西哥人。","en":"I'm Mexican.","r":"Wǒ shì Mòxīgē rén.","a":"n_055348cdfe4f.mp3"},{"t":"我们得谈谈。","en":"We need to talk.","r":"Wǒmen děi tántan.","a":"n_43077c647817.mp3"},{"t":"回来这儿。","en":"Come back here.","r":"Huílái zhèr.","a":"n_6fff6865f08b.mp3"},{"t":"在刮风。","en":"It's windy.","r":"Zài guāfēng.","a":"n_7e9265df75dd.mp3"},{"t":"现在就做。","en":"Do it now.","r":"Xiànzài jiù zuò.","a":"n_37bcc65e5499.mp3"},{"t":"我会游泳。","en":"I know how to swim.","r":"Wǒ huì yóuyǒng.","a":"n_037b47d191ad.mp3"},{"t":"你会开车吗？","en":"Do you know how to drive?","r":"Nǐ huì kāichē ma?","a":"n_05ac5d12f54c.mp3"},{"t":"你睡得好吗？","en":"Do you sleep well?","r":"Nǐ shuì de hǎo ma?","a":"n_c3be52059166.mp3"},{"t":"算我请客。","en":"It's on me.","r":"Suàn wǒ qǐngkè.","a":"n_ef29b3efc77c.mp3"},{"t":"我在这儿拐吗？","en":"Do I turn here?","r":"Wǒ zài zhèr guǎi ma?","a":"n_8db39be45bbf.mp3"},{"t":"可以，你能行。","en":"Yes, you can.","r":"Kěyǐ, nǐ néng xíng.","a":"n_c4d5ed000db2.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道。","en":"I don't know (it).","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào.","a":"n_c5c38478cd95.mp3"},{"t":"我回家了。","en":"I'm going home.","r":"Wǒ huíjiā le.","a":"n_d25a8c64426d.mp3"},{"t":"我在家。","en":"I'm home.","r":"Wǒ zài jiā.","a":"n_3eb40aef0223.mp3"},{"t":"我不喜欢。","en":"I don't like it.","r":"Wǒ bù xǐhuan.","a":"n_ee6db9e56685.mp3"},{"t":"我特别喜欢。","en":"I really like it.","r":"Wǒ tèbié xǐhuan.","a":"n_d9e5f1162ed6.mp3"},{"t":"我不太好。","en":"I'm not okay.","r":"Wǒ bú tài hǎo.","a":"n_a8f32aee8538.mp3"},{"t":"我特别好。","en":"I'm really good.","r":"Wǒ tèbié hǎo.","a":"n_dde85f230e62.mp3"},{"t":"我受不了了。","en":"I can't take any more.","r":"Wǒ shòubuliǎo le.","a":"n_298b785242dc.mp3"},{"t":"我想喝杯咖啡。","en":"I want a coffee.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng hē bēi kāfēi.","a":"n_4b561784d5f3.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都不要。","en":"I don't want anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu bú yào.","a":"n_db6fac73dd53.mp3"},{"t":"我去吃饭。","en":"I'm going to eat.","r":"Wǒ qù chīfàn.","a":"n_3ab94ee00a3f.mp3"},{"t":"现在一点了。","en":"It's one o'clock.","r":"Xiànzài yì diǎn le.","a":"n_4b8b156dd49c.mp3"},{"t":"真的很晚了。","en":"It's really late.","r":"Zhēn de hěn wǎn le.","a":"n_d0bb690ee9e4.mp3"},{"t":"我现在不行。","en":"I can't right now.","r":"Wǒ xiànzài bùxíng.","a":"n_b97a5aed5806.mp3"},{"t":"他是哪里人？","en":"Where's he from?","r":"Tā shì nǎlǐ rén?","a":"n_922897d36d20.mp3"},{"t":"特别疼。","en":"It hurts a lot.","r":"Tèbié téng.","a":"n_54b4dcf6a6ab.mp3"},{"t":"这里疼吗？","en":"Does it hurt here?","r":"Zhèlǐ téng ma?","a":"n_716ce5162c7b.mp3"},{"t":"你现在有空吗？","en":"Do you have time right now?","r":"Nǐ xiànzài yǒu kòng ma?","a":"n_08b2a30c271f.mp3"},{"t":"我在家工作。","en":"I work from home.","r":"Wǒ zài jiā gōngzuò.","a":"n_42bbf529eb53.mp3"},{"t":"我去上班。","en":"I'm going to work.","r":"Wǒ qù shàngbān.","a":"n_0afb2e10ccf5.mp3"},{"t":"我是本地人。","en":"I'm from here.","r":"Wǒ shì běndì rén.","a":"n_a42abe3eb9ac.mp3"},{"t":"我想做点什么。","en":"I want to do something.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng zuò diǎn shénme.","a":"n_ab9059c47931.mp3"},{"t":"我不累。","en":"I'm not tired.","r":"Wǒ bú lèi.","a":"n_ba4b84e75375.mp3"},{"t":"我太累了。","en":"I'm so tired.","r":"Wǒ tài lèi le.","a":"n_ff4b27e598f2.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都没做。","en":"I'm not doing anything.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu méi zuò.","a":"n_84721859a160.mp3"},{"t":"我现在该怎么办？","en":"What do I do now?","r":"Wǒ xiànzài gāi zěnme bàn?","a":"n_fa14efdff301.mp3"},{"t":"我觉得不是。","en":"I don't think so.","r":"Wǒ juéde bú shì.","a":"n_0f15a6fcef12.mp3"},{"t":"我在家吃饭。","en":"I eat at home.","r":"Wǒ zài jiā chīfàn.","a":"n_dd6da3e021f6.mp3"},{"t":"我边吃边工作。","en":"I eat and work.","r":"Wǒ biān chī biān gōngzuò.","a":"n_8a8f01ff6573.mp3"},{"t":"我去睡觉了。","en":"I'm going to sleep.","r":"Wǒ qù shuìjiào le.","a":"n_af881e9f79be.mp3"},{"t":"我想再睡会儿。","en":"I want to sleep more.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng zài shuì huìr.","a":"n_e23300019a32.mp3"},{"t":"我睡不着。","en":"I can't sleep.","r":"Wǒ shuì bu zháo.","a":"n_b161a819d01e.mp3"},{"t":"我能吃这个吗？","en":"Can I eat this?","r":"Wǒ néng chī zhège ma?","a":"n_2399e7d387d7.mp3"},{"t":"我要出去。","en":"I'm going to go out.","r":"Wǒ yào chūqù.","a":"n_550f7500fcf0.mp3"},{"t":"我得多睡会儿。","en":"I need to sleep more.","r":"Wǒ děi duō shuì huìr.","a":"n_c5b150a7c1d2.mp3"},{"t":"我得走了。","en":"I have to go.","r":"Wǒ děi zǒu le.","a":"n_e8843c4636ee.mp3"},{"t":"我非得去吗？","en":"Do I have to go?","r":"Wǒ fēiděi qù ma?","a":"n_3d552a7c7be5.mp3"},{"t":"几点了？","en":"What time is it?","r":"Jǐ diǎn le?","a":"n_f09e10216f27.mp3"},{"t":"你那边几点了？","en":"What time do you have?","r":"Nǐ nàbiān jǐ diǎn le?","a":"n_42ea7d5d6640.mp3"},{"t":"你想吃什么？","en":"What do you want to eat?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng chī shénme?","a":"n_3a30b55fcc34.mp3"},{"t":"你想做什么？","en":"What do you want to do?","r":"Nǐ xiǎng zuò shénme?","a":"n_f1f2c6f58c3d.mp3"},{"t":"我们回家吧。","en":"Let's go home.","r":"Wǒmen huíjiā ba.","a":"n_302e832f5094.mp3"},{"t":"我坐公交去。","en":"I'm going by bus.","r":"Wǒ zuò gōngjiāo qù.","a":"n_9cb51dcef999.mp3"},{"t":"我得工作。","en":"I have to work.","r":"Wǒ děi gōngzuò.","a":"n_516fb87261e4.mp3"},{"t":"她懂得很多。","en":"She knows a lot.","r":"Tā dǒng de hěn duō.","a":"n_98a51fa84ff4.mp3"},{"t":"我感觉很好。","en":"I feel good.","r":"Wǒ gǎnjué hěn hǎo.","a":"n_b86fa8ffd91f.mp3"},{"t":"你是哪里人？","en":"Where are you from?","r":"Nǐ shì nǎlǐ rén?","a":"n_8515b1d0cb7b.mp3"},{"t":"我真的好冷。","en":"I'm really cold.","r":"Wǒ zhēn de hǎo lěng.","a":"n_b090716638bd.mp3"},{"t":"太冷了。","en":"It's very cold.","r":"Tài lěng le.","a":"n_88ccee805fe9.mp3"},{"t":"谁说的？","en":"Who said that?","r":"Shéi shuō de?","a":"n_6c541e8aa475.mp3"},{"t":"你知道现在几点吗？","en":"Do you know the time?","r":"Nǐ zhīdào xiànzài jǐ diǎn ma?","a":"n_c8ba7221574b.mp3"},{"t":"你会煮咖啡吗？","en":"Do you know how to make coffee?","r":"Nǐ huì zhǔ kāfēi ma?","a":"n_8b4bcfd9958e.mp3"},{"t":"很近。","en":"It's very close.","r":"Hěn jìn.","a":"n_0b3fe8e6242e.mp3"}]}